If you want to do some test with NGINX!
---------------------------------------

1: Install nginx with this command:

brew install nginx
---------------------------------------


2: Prepare directory for testing:

- Create the directory --> /var/www/website/

- Create the directory --> /var/log/www/website

----------------------------------------

3: Now use make:

make update: copy the website content to the /var/log/www/website. 
--> Do it the first time you run and each time you modify the website content

make: run nginx

make stop: stop nginx

make re: reload nginx

-----------------------------------------

Now use browser to go to localhost:4242 for testing the website

Note:

- POST and DELETE method in the website work only on the localhost:4242

- When you testing our code, make stop for free the port 4242 from nginx
